{"tid":1321191,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔該收埋你d英國美國法國國旗","createTime":"2019-07-15T15:07:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T15:35:52.000Z","uid":123713,"like":4,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a9653a7beebf9db3719e70348c8931874a841558","tid":1321191,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T15:07:04.000Z","msg":"次次遊行都有人揮旗<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中華民國都叫做勉強扯上關係<br />\n1.香港上世紀既不平等條約仲係台北保管緊<br />\n2.雖然有92共識 但台灣仲聲稱緊中國係台灣不可分割既一部份<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><br />\n但其他國旗係做乜尻？<br />\n尋日沙田仲支法國 我真係黑人問號<br />\n<br />\n英國美國 兩個利益掛帥既國家<br />\n你唔撚係望佢會救你下話？<br />\n</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n揮旗就象徵意義大於實際意義<br />\n但拎其他國家既旗<br />\n只會連輿論都輸撚埋 不如唔好拎<br />\n拎返張poster講五大訴求好過<br />\n<br />\n你要反中共<br />\n一係整支香港旗 唔係港英旗<br />\n一係拎中華民國 憲法上都講得過去 <br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">其他國家冇任何旗可以代表2019年6月以後既香港</span></span></strong>！"},{"pid":"839502128e4533919e7e7e3f2c790dc5b00c76aa","tid":1321191,"uid":95102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T15:07:36.000Z","msg":"唔好意思阻你少少位<br />\n我打咗份聲明俾721嘅義士宣讀<br />\n希望各位巴打可以入嚟幫手改下<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n=========================<br />\n<br />\n721衝之前應該要搵人開記者會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1320570\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1320570</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n========================="},{"pid":"29cde2d0b9a2a3a4454ad100d47331e5a748351f","tid":1321191,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T15:13:33.000Z","msg":"英國: 中英聯合聲明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"accccbd0a26f4cb1c29c57da2eca22a3bd9735e4","tid":1321191,"uid":191815,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"